<reg_public_text>:
Configure common forwarding options. 

Upon reception of a frame the (DMAC, EFID) is used to perform a lookup in the MAC table. If an entry is found the destination is known and forwarded according to the entry ADDR_TYPE and ADDR. Alternatively the destination is considered unknown and might be applicable for flooding.
